text.tspan: Discards are animals thrown back (alive or dead) into the sea after being caught during fishing activities.
This represents bycatch (fish caught unintentionally) that is not brought ashore for use.
Data source: FishStat via Pauly, Zeller, and Palomares from Sea Around Us Concepts, Design and Data.
